data.name: label1.Text
data.value:
GeoGen Studio has encountered an unrecoverable fatal error and the application had to be terminated.
The currently opened document was saved as emergencyBackup.nut into GeoGen data directory (where the "examples" directory is located).
Please copy following error information and send it to the email address found in the Help -> About dialog along with short description of how the error occured. Reported errors will be fixed as soon as possible.
